[h4 
	" Boss: Thanos
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"The most difficult boss fight of the game, mainly because he is the only character in the game that can block. If you keep comboing him he will block and if you don't knock him down he will also block, in short any strategy that you shouldn't use against other bosses you must use against him.
	$LF
